# 🏨 Hotel Rate Comparator API

The **Hotel Rate Comparator** is a microservice-based backend service that compares hotel prices from multiple suppliers (Supplier A and Supplier B) and returns the best available rates. It uses [Temporal.io](https://temporal.io) to orchestrate parallel external API calls, deduplicate hotel data by name, and respond with the most cost-effective options.

## ✨ Features

- Parallel API calls to multiple hotel suppliers
- Smart deduplication of hotel listings by name
- Best-rate comparison algorithm
- Temporal.io workflow orchestration
- Docker container support
- AWS ECS deployment ready

